{"title":"大地","authors":["金珠玉"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":5,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京铁路局  金珠玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，那条生硬的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该怎样回首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去拾取痛惜的回忆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有忘掉！是因为："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾庄严地在一排领袖的画像前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行过第一次队礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，党的领袖，开国元老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一年的新春，不曾怀着崇敬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把您们的画像擦净，挂起？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限的恨啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在突然倒挂的名字下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我失去了对您的敬意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象浪子回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回首云雾过处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您竟离去，无声无息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史记得您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的丰碑就是您钟爱的大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对祖国大地我们宣誓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了明天，从我做起！……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}